    <title>linux 操作</title>
    <url>/2020/09/18/linux%20Shell%20%E5%88%9D%E5%AD%A6/</url>
    <content><![CDATA[<h1 id="1-Grep"><a href="#1-Grep" class="headerlink" title="1.Grep"></a>1.Grep</h1><p>暂时没怎么用到 先做个记录吧  万一以后用到了<br>grep命令的常用格式为：grep  [选项]  ”模式“  [文件]<br>grep家族总共有三个：grep，egrep，fgrep。<br><strong>常用选项：</strong><br>　　-E ：开启扩展（Extend）的正则表达式。<br>　　-i ：忽略大小写（ignore case）。<br>　　-v ：反过来（invert），只打印没有匹配的，而匹配的反而不打印。<br>　　-n ：显示行号<br>　　-w ：被匹配的文本只能是单词，而不能是单词中的某一部分，如文本中有liker，而我搜寻的只是like，就可以使用-w选项来避免匹配liker<br>　　-c ：显示总共有多少行被匹配到了，而不是显示被匹配到的内容，注意如果同时使用-cv选项是显示有多少行没有被匹配到。<br>　　-o ：只显示被模式匹配到的字符串。<br>　　–color :将匹配到的内容以颜色高亮显示。<br>　　-A  n：显示匹配到的字符串所在的行及其后n行，after<br>　　-B  n：显示匹配到的字符串所在的行及其前n行，before<br>　　-C  n：显示匹配到的字符串所在的行及其前后各n行，context<br>1、直接输入要匹配的字符串，这个可以用fgrep（fast grep）代替来提高查找速度，比如我要匹配一下hello.c文件中printf的个数：fgrep  -c  “printf”  hello.c<br>2、使用基本正则表达式，下面谈关于基本正则表达式的使用：<br><strong>匹配字符：</strong><br>　　　　            . ：任意一个字符。<br>　　　　　     [abc] ：表示匹配一个字符，这个字符必须是abc中的一个。<br>　　　　　     [a-zA-Z] ：表示匹配一个字符，这个字符必须是a-z或A-Z这52个字母中的一个。<br>　　　　　　[^123] ：匹配一个字符，这个字符是除了1、2、3以外的所有字符。<br>　　　　　　对于一些常用的字符集，系统做了定义：<br>　　　　　　[A-Za-z] 等价于 [[:alpha:]]<br>　　　　　　[0-9] 等价于 [[:digit:]]<br>　　　　　　[A-Za-z0-9] 等价于 [[:alnum:]]<br>　　　　　　tab,space 等空白字符 [[:space:]]<br>　　　　　　[A-Z] 等价于 [[:upper:]]<br>　　　　　　[a-z] 等价于 [[:lower:]]<br>　　　　　　标点符号 [[:punct:]]<br><strong>匹配次数：</strong><br>　　　　　　{m,n} ：匹配其前面出现的字符至少m次，至多n次。<br>　　　　　　? ：匹配其前面出现的内容0次或1次，等价于{0,1}。<br>　　　　　　* ：匹配其前面出现的内容任意次，等价于{0,}，所以 “.*” 表述任意字符任意次，即无论什么内容全部匹配。<br><strong>位置锚定：</strong><br>　　　　　　^ ：锚定行首<br>　　　　　　$ ：锚定行尾。技巧：”^$”用于匹配空白行。<br>　　　　　　\b或&lt;：锚定单词的词首。如”\blike”不会匹配alike，但是会匹配liker<br>　　　　　　\b或&gt;：锚定单词的词尾。如”\blike\b”不会匹配alike和liker，只会匹配like<br>　　　　　　\B ：与\b作用相反。</p>
<h1 id="2-awk"><a href="#2-awk" class="headerlink" title="2.awk"></a>2.awk</h1><p>目前只用到一个</p>
<figure class="highlight powershell"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">game_id=<span class="variable">$</span>(<span class="built_in">echo</span> <span class="variable">$line</span> | awk <span class="string">&#x27;&#123;print $1&#125;&#x27;</span>)</span><br><span class="line">url=<span class="variable">$</span>(<span class="built_in">echo</span> <span class="variable">$line</span> | awk <span class="string">&#x27;&#123;print $2&#125;&#x27;</span>)</span><br><span class="line"></span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>
<p>默认用空格分隔 分别获取第一个第二个字符 可以用-F’a’ ，a为符号，改选定a分割 </p>
<h1 id="3-其他七七八八"><a href="#3-其他七七八八" class="headerlink" title="3.其他七七八八"></a>3.其他七七八八</h1><p>把目前写的一个shell 贴上来，到时候可以看看哈哈哈哈 </p>
<figure class="highlight powershell"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="comment">#!/bin/bash</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="keyword">if</span> [[ <span class="variable">$</span>(<span class="type">uname</span> -<span class="type">s</span>) == <span class="string">&quot;Darwin&quot;</span> ]]; then</span><br><span class="line">    alias date=<span class="string">&quot;gdate&quot;</span></span><br><span class="line">    alias <span class="built_in">echo</span>=<span class="string">&quot;gecho&quot;</span></span><br><span class="line">fi</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">source ../utils.sh</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">ScheduleTime=<span class="variable">$</span>(get_azkaban_prop <span class="string">&quot;ScheduleTime&quot;</span>)</span><br><span class="line"><span class="comment"># 从ScheduleTime中获取当前时间</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="keyword">if</span> [[ -<span class="type">z</span> <span class="string">&quot;<span class="variable">$ScheduleTime</span>&quot;</span> ]]; then</span><br><span class="line">    now=<span class="variable">$</span>(date <span class="literal">-d</span> <span class="string">&quot;1 day ago&quot;</span> +<span class="string">&quot;%Y-%m-%d&quot;</span>)</span><br><span class="line"><span class="keyword">else</span></span><br><span class="line">    now=<span class="variable">$</span>(date <span class="literal">-d</span> <span class="string">&quot;<span class="variable">$ScheduleTime</span> 1 day ago&quot;</span> +<span class="string">&quot;%Y-%m-%d&quot;</span>)</span><br><span class="line">fi</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line"><span class="comment"># 可以提供一个参数表示跑当前时间的数据</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="keyword">if</span> [[ ! -<span class="type">z</span> <span class="variable">$1</span> ]]; then</span><br><span class="line">    now=<span class="string">&quot;<span class="variable">$1</span>&quot;</span></span><br><span class="line">fi</span><br><span class="line"><span class="comment">#将时间传给python文件,这里有一个注意的是如果只访问同一天的话那么起止时间应该是一样的</span></span><br><span class="line">dt=<span class="variable">$</span>(date <span class="literal">-d</span><span class="string">&quot;<span class="variable">$now</span>&quot;</span> +<span class="string">&quot;%Y%m%d&quot;</span>)</span><br><span class="line">from_ts=<span class="variable">$</span>[<span class="variable">$</span>(<span class="type">date</span> -<span class="type">d</span><span class="string">&quot;<span class="variable">$dt</span>&quot;</span> +<span class="string">&quot;%s&quot;</span>)+<span class="number">28800</span>]</span><br><span class="line">end_ts=<span class="variable">$</span>[<span class="variable">$</span>(<span class="type">date</span> -<span class="type">d</span><span class="string">&quot;<span class="variable">$dt</span>&quot;</span> +<span class="string">&quot;%s&quot;</span>)+<span class="number">28800</span>]</span><br><span class="line"><span class="comment">#文件名暂时以时间命名 </span></span><br><span class="line">dt_links=<span class="string">&quot;<span class="variable">$</span>&#123;dt&#125;.txt&quot;</span></span><br><span class="line">run_with_check <span class="string">&quot;python3 ga_data.py <span class="variable">$from_ts</span> <span class="variable">$end_ts</span> <span class="variable">$dt_links</span>&quot;</span></span><br><span class="line">dest_dir=<span class="string">&quot;oss://joypac-data/ga_log/&quot;</span></span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">workdir=<span class="variable">$</span>(<span class="built_in">cd</span> <span class="variable">$</span>(dirname <span class="variable">$0</span>); <span class="built_in">pwd</span>)</span><br><span class="line">mkdir <span class="literal">-p</span> <span class="variable">$workdir</span>/<span class="keyword">data</span>/<span class="variable">$dt</span></span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line"><span class="function"><span class="keyword">function</span> <span class="title">httpfile_to_oss</span><span class="params">()</span></span>&#123;</span><br><span class="line">    <span class="built_in">echo</span> <span class="variable">$1</span></span><br><span class="line">    local_linksfile=<span class="string">&quot;<span class="variable">$1</span>&quot;</span></span><br><span class="line">    <span class="built_in">echo</span> <span class="string">&quot;<span class="variable">$local_linksfile</span>&quot;</span></span><br><span class="line">    <span class="built_in">cat</span> <span class="variable">$local_linksfile</span> | <span class="keyword">while</span> read line</span><br><span class="line">    <span class="keyword">do</span></span><br><span class="line">	<span class="built_in">cd</span> <span class="variable">$workdir</span>/<span class="keyword">data</span>/<span class="variable">$dt</span></span><br><span class="line">        game_id=<span class="variable">$</span>(<span class="built_in">echo</span> <span class="variable">$line</span> | awk <span class="string">&#x27;&#123;print $1&#125;&#x27;</span>)</span><br><span class="line">	url=<span class="variable">$</span>(<span class="built_in">echo</span> <span class="variable">$line</span> | awk <span class="string">&#x27;&#123;print $2&#125;&#x27;</span>)</span><br><span class="line">	<span class="comment">#echo $game_id</span></span><br><span class="line">        <span class="comment">#echo ID:$lastgame_id</span></span><br><span class="line">	<span class="comment">#echo url:$url</span></span><br><span class="line">	name=<span class="variable">$</span>(basename <span class="variable">$url</span>)</span><br><span class="line">	file=<span class="variable">$</span>&#123;name%<span class="string">&#x27;?&#x27;</span>*&#125;</span><br><span class="line">	<span class="comment">#name=$&#123;url%&#x27;?&#x27;*&#125;</span></span><br><span class="line">        <span class="comment">#file=$&#123;name##*/&#125;</span></span><br><span class="line">	<span class="comment">#echo $file</span></span><br><span class="line">	json_name=<span class="variable">$</span>&#123;file%<span class="string">&#x27;.&#x27;</span>*&#125;</span><br><span class="line">	<span class="built_in">echo</span> json_name:<span class="variable">$json_name</span></span><br><span class="line">        gz_name=<span class="variable">$game_id</span>-<span class="variable">$file</span></span><br><span class="line">	<span class="built_in">echo</span> gz_name: <span class="variable">$gz_name</span></span><br><span class="line">        <span class="comment">#wget -c -O $gz_name $url</span></span><br><span class="line">	run_with_check <span class="string">&quot;wget -c -O <span class="variable">$gz_name</span>  \&quot;</span><span class="variable">$url</span>\<span class="string">&quot;&quot;</span></span><br><span class="line">  	gzip <span class="literal">-d</span> <span class="variable">$gz_name</span></span><br><span class="line">        <span class="built_in">cat</span> <span class="variable">$game_id</span>-<span class="variable">$json_name</span> &gt; <span class="variable">$game_id</span>-<span class="variable">$dt</span>.json</span><br><span class="line">	<span class="built_in">rm</span> <span class="literal">-rf</span> <span class="variable">$game_id</span>-<span class="variable">$json_name</span></span><br><span class="line">    done</span><br><span class="line">    run_with_check <span class="string">&quot;ossutil64 cp -r  <span class="variable">$workdir</span>/data  <span class="variable">$dest_dir</span>&quot;</span></span><br><span class="line">    <span class="comment">#删除本地数据</span></span><br><span class="line">    <span class="built_in">rm</span> <span class="literal">-rf</span> <span class="variable">$workdir</span>/<span class="keyword">data</span>/*</span><br><span class="line">    <span class="built_in">rm</span> <span class="literal">-rf</span> <span class="variable">$workdir</span>/<span class="variable">$local_linksfile</span></span><br><span class="line">&#125;</span><br><span class="line">httpfile_to_oss <span class="variable">$dt_links</span></span><br><span class="line"></span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>
<p>先这样吧  </p>
]]></content>
